The Abia governorship candidate of National Rescue Movement (NRM),  Dr. Kalu Ijioma Ukeh has picked Nnamdi Eze Ireaja, an Engineer, as his running mate.   Speaking on the choice of Eze,Ukeh said he decided to pick someone who understands the problem of the state and the country at large, whose experience in various sphere of life is overwhelming.  “Ireaja is a man of undaunted good quality personality and will help to bring the needed impetus to bear on the development of the state if we are elected by Abians”.